---
title: Smoky Gochujang and BBQ Bacon and Bean Jacky-P with Cheese and Sesame Slaw
description: Jacket potatoes aren't just for baked beans and cheese. Our Smoky Gochujang and BBQ Bean Jacky-P is a spicy, Korean inspired twist on the humble jacket potato for a comforting weeknight dinner.
